\id TIT Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h TITUS
\toc1 TITUS
\toc2 Titus
\toc3 Tit
\mt1 TITUS CAPAT
\mt4 (Letter to Titus)
\is2 TITUS CAPAT KAWNG
\im Paul loh Titus he Asia Minor neh Greek ah a om vaengkah bibipuei la puetpuet a thui (2 Kor 2.13; 7.6,13; 8.6,16,23; 12.18; Galati 2.3). Paul loh Titu taengah Crete kah bibikung rhoek te tuek a ti nah.
\ip Khrihca hlangboel kah mawtkung neh bibikung rhoek tah khoboethen neh awtkoi la om saeh (chapter 1.5-9). Boeipa kah hnukbang rhoek boeih tah cue uh saeh lamtah oeltaihnah rhael saeh (1.10—2.9).
\ip Crete kah hlangcom hlangcae boeih te Paul loh ol a uen. Hingnah longpuei thai he tah Pathen loh Jesuh Khrih han tueih dongah ni. Pathen loh hlang hing a khang, a silh tih dungyan hingah, ngaiuepnah a paek. (3.4,5). Titus capat he AD 65 vaengah a tael.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 Titus ham kuttuknah neh thangthuinah \ior (1. 1-4)\ior*
\io1 Hlangboel Bibikung ham oluennah \ior (1. 5-16)\ior*
\io1 Hlangboel rhaengpuei ham oluennah \ior (2. 1—3. 11)\ior*
\io1 Hnukkhueng kah oluennah \ior (3. 12-15)\ior*
